%section.phone

%section.explanation
  %h2
    Ever forget to change the order
    %br
    of your Netflix queue?
  %h2
    Does a movie show up
    %br
    you no longer want?

- content_for :bottom do
  #form-backer

  / we need to stick in the rails form later
  = form_tag '/auth/netflix', id: 'signup' do

    %label Send me a reminder email every:
    %ul.days
      %li.day Mon
      %li.day Tue
      %li.day.selected Wed
      %li.day Thu
      %li.day Fri
      %li.day Sat
      %li.day Sun

    %label at this email address:
    %input{type: "text", placeholder: "email address"}
    
    %input{type: "submit", value: "Authorize Netflix access"}
  
    %p
      We send you a weekly email of your upcoming movies.
      %br
      Happy with what you're getting next? Leave it.
      %br
      Prefer one of your other movies? Choose it.